---THE STORY:


   The planet Eotcatcit has been invaded by the Extermination Alliance,
an evil orginization determined to conquer the universe.  The Alliance has
wiped out the entire TicTacToe Defense Force except for the two greatest
warriors, Mr. X and Mr. O.  Mr. X and Mr. O must wipe out the invasion force
of Slimeys, Flameys, Iceys, and Fisheys; and must then use the Model XWB-95J
Space Warp Booster/Wormhole Stabilizer® from IPM Enterprises to go to the 
four home planets of the invasion force in order to annihilate their armies 
so they won't be able to retake the planet.


---THE CONTROLS:


   Player 1 controls Mr. X.  Use a joystick in port 2 to move him in 8
directions and the fire button to fire in direction of movement.  Player 1 
can go anywhere on the left half of the screen.

   Player 2 controls Mr. O.  Use a joystick in port 1.  Press the fire button
after the game begins to activate two-player mode.  Player 2 can go anywhere 
on the right half of the screen.

   To exit to Workbench, simply click the top left-hand corner of the title 
screen.


---YOUR ENEMIES:

   
   · Slimey (100 pts) - Slow moving slime creature that spits slimeballs at
you.

   · Flamey (100 pts) - Walking flame that tries to ram you.

   · Icey (100 pts) - Quick miniature snowman that chuks iceballs at you.

   · Fishey (100 pts) - Robotic fish that launches torpedoes.

   · GT-400 HiPower Cannon® (500 pts) - Armored cannon--fires powerful laser 
blasts.

   · D-21 IceDrone® (300 pts) - Slides down ice river and fires iceballs.

   · GT-609 IslandSniper® (400 pts) - Rapid fire random gun situated on 
islands.

   · Super Slimey (1000 pts) - Giant slime creature armed with slimeball
bursts.

   · HC-819 MegaBlaster® (700 pts per section) Heavily armored, fast moving 
hovercraft with tons of firepower.

   · GT-911 TurboLaser®  (1000 pts) - Mobile laser cannon that moves at 
lightning speed back and forth.

   
   *® HiPower Cannon, IceDrone, IslandSniper, MegaBlaster, and TurboLaser are
registered trademarks of Destruction Inc., the official manufacturing company
of the Extermination Alliance.


---ENEMIES ON PLANETS:


   LEVEL 1 (Planet Eotcatcit) - Slimey, Flamey, Icey, Fishey, and GT-400.  
