---NOTES:

   When you first play the game, you may notice that your craft can only go 
halfway across the screen.  This is NOT a bug!!!  This is the way I designed
the game!  Each player is limited to their own half of the screen because of
TTTDF Rules of Engagement regarding placing extra drain on the XWB-95J.

   
